{"tid":1510780,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"全民振興經濟行動","createTime":"2019-08-27T10:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T09:05:21.000Z","uid":52152,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"12816d1dd1f0949df3d795c4ac34b0c3c323155c","tid":1510780,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:07:39.000Z","msg":"政府成日話因為我哋搞到經濟下滑又話好難回復又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我打算搞一個振興經濟行動去刺激消費，希望大家俾啲意見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RJ4PyOB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRJ4PyOB.png&h=66ca3330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要刺激經濟最好既做法梗係多消費，<span style=\"color: red;\">可以俾我哋盡情消費既地方一定係商場喇</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前有好多商家佬登曬報紙話自己好慘，香港人梗係要幫下佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">不過如果大家覺得唔啱心水既話，我哋係唔會強迫消費架</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n服飾：唔一定黑色既，最緊要舒服，話曬行街shopping可以搞好耐架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n裝備：大旅行喼(萬一買好多野都唔怕)<br />\n注意事項：小心喼會撞親同路人，唔好因為有爭執而影響人流喇[/red]<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望其他巴打俾下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n831 民陣遊行<br />\n901 機場"},{"pid":"17f572185087781925f3fec73b5fef13f4aae84f","tid":1510780,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"商場戰"},{"pid":"6af8600a76c5830fd6411458f66aa047c47d26cf","tid":1510780,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:52:52.000Z","msg":"我諗依個係唔傷到手足又可以直擊商家佬既方法"},{"pid":"af850ddcb173380f14eaf252246f051368b0b7bb","tid":1510780,"uid":1747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:06:03.000Z","msg":"第一個攬炒活動上線？"},{"pid":"73e4ed45b61435caaad419469a94e8f9fcf8a02f","tid":1510780,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dis